      "text": "The patterns community is quite big on this idea:  software design being a communication media, e.g. the PLoP conference. Also here's one piece you might enjoy: [https://homepages.ecs.vuw.ac.nz/~kjx/papers/e03.pdf pdf] -- @stephenrkell [https://twitter.com/stephenrkell/status/1454030584582443015 twitter]"
